WEBVTT

00:02:59.122 --> 00:03:00.633
Just look at how many languages

00:03:00.657 --> 00:03:02.930
they translate their
marketing material into.

00:03:03.677 --> 00:03:06.338
They make pamphlets,
radio shows and videos

00:03:06.362 --> 00:03:08.335
in not just English and Arabic,

00:03:08.359 --> 00:03:13.126
but German, Russian,
French, Turkish, Kurdish,

00:03:13.150 --> 00:03:14.822
Hebrew,

00:03:14.846 --> 00:03:16.587
Mandarin Chinese.

00:03:17.309 --> 00:03:21.501
I've even seen an ISIS-produced
video in sign language.

00:03:22.605 --> 00:03:24.489
Just think about that for a second:

00:03:24.513 --> 00:03:26.821
ISIS took the time and made the effort

00:03:26.845 --> 00:03:30.649
to ensure their message is reaching
the deaf and hard of hearing.